=version 1
=resource Shop
=method get
=endpoint /shop/categories/:id/items
=description Lists items in a shop category.

include ../../_mixins.jade

p This lists the items that belong to a particular category. Keep in mind that items can belong to multiple categories, so there may be overlap if you request multiple categories.

table.endpoint-param-table
    tr
        td.name :id
        td.description Category ID to search in.
    tr
        td.name order #[span optional]
        td.description
            p Specifies the order in which items should be displayed in the format #[code attribute:order]. Order should be one of #[code asc] or #[code desc]. Attribute may be one of:
            ul
                li id
                li title
                li description
                li purchases
                li currency_cost
                li points_cost
                li max_per_user
                li max_quantity
                li createdAt
                li updatedAt

            p If the attribute or order do not follow these rules, that sorting rule will be ignored.

